# Glaze documentation

Welcome! This is the main documentation hub for Glaze.

Glaze is a fast, modern PHP static site generator built for people who like clean files and quick iteration.

It combines:

- [Djot](https://djot.net/) for expressive modern markup
- [Djot](https://djot.net/) for expressive modern markup (powered by [php-collective/djot-php](https://github.com/php-collective/djot-php))
- [Sugar](https://josbeir.github.io/sugar/) for clean, component-friendly PHP templating
- a simple content + template workflow that feels lightweight but powerful

Write in modern markup, render with modern PHP templates, and ship static output fast.

